SUMMARY:Spring Blossoms Stroll in Montavilla w Optional Lunch
DESCRIPTION:The Portland Hiking Meetup Group\nHi everyone! Spring is here and so are the flowers. Let's take a walk around a nice quiet neighborhood with plenty of blooming plants to look at. We may also see a Portland Heritage Tree of two. We will meet at Roscoe's to begin our walk. We will stroll around for a couple of hours and taking in the sights. After this\, we can head back to Roscoe's for some food and drinks. Please come out and meet some new folks\, get outside and get some exercise. See ya there!
