SUMMARY:Washington Park/Thru Hoyt 
DESCRIPTION:The Portland Hiking Meetup Group\nOur group meets near the base of steps leading up into the park\, by the parking lot on the uphill side of the tennis courts. Expect a fairly fast pace on trails with plenty of elevation gain.
